  <description><![CDATA[<p><strong>Sleeps: 8 Guests.</strong></p>
<p>Chalet Ariondaz is a bright apartment chalet, superbly located for the shops and slopes of Courchevel 1650.</p>
<p>Located in the Chalets de la Mouria Résidence, it offers quality accommodation and easy access to the fantastic 1650 and 3 Valleys ski area with the 3 Vallées chairlift, about 6 minutes’ walk away. The chalet has a comfortable lounge and dining area with a log fire, perfect for relaxing in front of after a good day on the slopes. For those who want to explore the 1650 après-ski then it is just 2 minutes’ walk to the resort centre. The complex has a shared wellness area with a sauna and hot tub and sessions can be reserved locally (pay locally).</p>]]></description>
