  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Accommodation Summary</strong></p>
<p><strong>Ground Floor</strong><strong><br />Room 1:</strong> Twin with en suite shower.<strong><br />Room 2:</strong> Double with en suite shower.<br />Shared wc.</p>
<p><img src="/media/13057964/france_three-valleys-ski-area_courchevel_chalet-ariondaz_interior_ground-floor.jpg" alt="Chalet Ariondaz Ground Floor Floorplan" align="absmiddle" /></p>
<p><strong>First Floor<br /></strong>Lounge and dining area with log fire and balcony.</p>
<p><img src="/media/13057963/france_three-valleys-ski-area_courchevel_chalet-ariondaz_interior_first-floor.jpg" alt="Chalet Ariondaz First Floor Floorplan" align="absmiddle" /></p>
<p><strong>Second Floor</strong><strong><br />Room 3:</strong> Twin with private bath/wc (not en suite)<strong><br />Room 4:</strong> Twin with en suite shower/wc</p>
<p>N.B.: Floor plans are for guidance only and are not to scale.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
